data.description: **OFFER DEADLINE MON 5PM** This updated ranch, with its cozy atmosphere and modern amenities, eagerly awaits its next owners. Multiple points of entry provide flexibility. Through the front, an open plan living space with recessed lighting, hardwood floors, and a new wood stove. The living room transitions into an eat-in country kitchen, where modern charm meets functionality with tile flooring, granite counters, and stainless-steel appliances. Three comfortable bedrooms offer hardwood flooring, while the bathroom features ceramic tile floors and updated fixtures. First floor laundry off a center entrance! An oversized great room provides additional flex space. Outside, a spacious double+ lot includes a storage shed wired with electric, plenty of room for hobbies and storage. Parking is hassle-free with a resurfaced driveway and more gravel space as needed. Enjoy the privacy, safety & charm of a fully fenced yard on one side of the property with more natural wooded space on the other.
